data.title: Fall 2023 Dean's List Announced
data.meta_description: 2,093 students have been named to the Fall 2023 Dean's List at Kutztown University.
data.text:
KUTZTOWN, Pa. – 2,094 students have been named to the Fall 2023 Dean's List at Kutztown University. To be eligible for the Dean's List, an undergraduate student must be registered for at least 12 credits and have a minimum grade point average of 3.60.

Students who have requested privacy (FERPA) have not been listed.

Click here to see the list in a pdf format

Click here to view Kutztown University's Merit Page
